...a selection of Arduino, ChipKit, and dev boards...

<a href="http://blog.makerbar.com/?attachment_id=384" rel="attachment wp-att-384"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-384" alt="2012-10-23 22.08.45" src="http://blog.makerbar.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/2012-10-23-22.08.45-1024x768.jpg" width="620" height="465" /></a>

