&nbsp;

Been procrastinating? Well, pull your act together and show up before you miss out on even more excellence! <strong>The MakerBar is open every Wednesday and Friday, with free open-house events from 7:00 until midnight</strong>.

<a href="http://meetup.com/makerbar">Join us on Meetup</a>, <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/makerbar">follow us on Twitter</a>, and <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/makerbar">join our discussion group</a>, but most importantly, show up and see the MakerBar firsthand!
